\c 13
\p
\v 1 Uba kuvela phakathi kwakho umprofethi kumbe umphuphi wamaphupho\x + Zek. 10.2.\x*, akunike isibonakaliso loba isimangaliso\x + Mat. 7.22,23. 24.24. 2 Thes. 2.9,11. Isam. 13.14.\x*,
\v 2 lesibonakaliso loba isimangaliso akhulume ngaso kuwe senzakale, esithi: Asilandele abanye onkulunkulu ongabazanga, sibakhonze\x + 18.22. Jer. 28.9.\x*;
\v 3 ungalaleli amazwi alowomprofethi loba lowomphuphi wamaphupho; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu iyalilinga ukuze yazi ukuthi liyayithanda yini iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu ngenhliziyo yenu yonke langomphefumulo wenu wonke\x + 8.2.\x*.
\v 4 IN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu lizayilandela, yona liyesabe, imithetho yayo liyigcine, ilizwi layo lililalele, yona liyikhonze\x + 2 Kho. 23.3. 2 Lan. 34.31.\x*, kuyo linamathele\x + 10.20.\x*.
\v 5 Lalowomprofethi loba lowomphuphi wamaphupho kabulawe, ngoba ukhulume ukuhlamukela iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wenu, eyalikhupha elizweni leGibhithe, yakuhlenga endlini yobugqili\x + 18.20. Jer. 14.15. Zek. 13.3.\x*, ukukufuqa uphambuke endleleni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho eyakulaya ukuhamba ngayo\x + 13.5,10. 2 Kho. 17.21.\x*. Ngalokhu uzakhupha ububi phakathi kwakho\x + 17.7,12. 19.19. 21.21. 22.21,22,24. 24.7. 1 Kor. 5.13.\x*.
\p
\v 6 Uba umfowenu, indodana kanyoko, loba indodana yakho, loba indodakazi yakho\x + 17.2.\x*, loba umfazi wesifuba sakho, kumbe umngane wakho\x + 28.54,56. Mika 7.5.\x* onjengomphefumulo wakho, ekuyenga ensitha esithi: Asihambe, siyekhonza abanye onkulunkulu, ongabazanga, wena laboyihlo\x + 1 Sam. 18.1,3. 20.17.\x*,
\v 7 babonkulunkulu babantu abalizingelezeleyo, abaseduze lawe loba abakhatshana lawe, kusukela ko\add munye\add* umkhawulo womhlaba kuze kufike ko\add munye\add* umkhawulo womhlaba\x + 6.14.\x*,
\v 8 ungamvumeli, ungamlaleli\x + Zaga 1.10.\x*, futhi ilihlo lakho lingamhawukeli, njalo unga\add m\add*yekeli, ungamfihli\x + 7.16.\x*,
\v 9 kodwa umbulale lokumbulala; isandla sakho sizakuba ngesokuqala phezu kwakhe ukumbulala, lemva kwalokho isandla sabantu bonke\x + 17.7.\x*.
\v 10 Njalo mkhande ngamatshe aze afe\x + 17.5.\x*, ngoba ubedinga ukukufuqa uphambuke eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho, eyakukhupha elizweni leGibhithe, endlini yobugqili\x + 13.5,10; 2 Kho. 17.21.\x*.
\v 11 LoIsrayeli wonke uzakuzwa, esabe, angabe esenza ububi obunjengalobo phakathi kwakho\x + 17.13. 19.20.\x*.
\p
\v 12 Uba usizwa komunye wemizi yakho, iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekunika yona, ukuthi uhlale khona, kuthiwa\x + Josh. 22.11.\x*:
\v 13 Kuphumile amadoda, abantwana bakaBheliyali, phakathi kwakho, afuqa aphambula abakhileyo bomuzi wawo esithi: Asihambe siyekhonza abanye onkulunkulu elingabazanga;
\v 14 khona uzabuza, uhlolisise, udingisise; khangela, uba kuliqiniso, leyonto iqinisekile, lesisinengiso senziwe phakathi kwakho\x + 17.4. 19.18.\x*,
\v 15 uzatshaya lokubatshaya abakhileyo balowomuzi ngobukhali benkemba, uwutshabalalise, lakho konke okukuwo lezifuyo zawo, ngobukhali benkemba\x + Eks. 22.20. Josh. 6.17,21.\x*.
\v 16 Uzabuthela yonke impango yawo phakathi komdanga wawo, utshise ngomlilo umuzi lempango yawo yonke uphele du, eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho\x + Josh. 6.24.\x*; njalo uzakuba yinqumbi phakade, awuyikwakhiwa futhi\x + Josh. 8.28. Jer. 49.2.\x*.
\v 17 Kunganamatheli lutho kwalokho okuqalekisiweyo esandleni sakho, ukuze iN\nd kosi\nd* iphenduke ekuvutheni kwentukuthelo yayo, ikuphe umusa, ibe lobubele kuwe, ikwandise\x + Josh. 7.26.\x*, njengalokhu yafunga kuboyihlo\x + Gen. 22.16,17. Gen. 50.24.\x*,
\v 18 uba ulalela ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ukugcina yonke imithetho yayo engikulaya yona lamuhla, ukwenza okulungileyo emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho\x + 12.25,28.\x*.